efault password behavior\n- `UserDetailsServiceAutoConfiguration` default `InMemoryUserDetailsManager`\n- backing off when a custom `UserDetailsService` is provided\n- servlet security auto-configuration default `SecurityFilterChain`\n- `DelegatingFilterProxyRegistrationBean` order, filter name, and dispatcher types\n- backing off when a custom `SecurityFilterChain` is provided\n- servlet `PathRequest` static resource matchers, including exclusions and selected locations\n- `SecurityFilterProperties` defaults and setters\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0129e3f9087b66fb016a3eed815b48819384e255e8968706a0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 636, "output": 1043, "cacheRead": 45568, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 47247, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782508914774, "responseId": "resp_0129e3f9087b66fb016a3eed7356348193a56eea863eca6726"}, "toolResults": []}
